<item>
            <title>[LUCENE-2370] Reintegrate flex branch into trunk</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/LUCENE-2370</link>
                <project id="12310110" key="LUCENE">Lucene - Core</project>
                        <description>&lt;p&gt;This issue is for reintegrating the flex branch into current trunk. I will post the patch here for review and commit, when all contributors to flex have reviewed the patch.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Before committing, I will tag both trunk and flex.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
